{"header":{"word":"שָׂפָה","entry":9507,"letter":"שׂ","strongs":8193,"page":973},"definitions":[{"title":"Def","body":" [[שָׂפָה]]:176 ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"n.f.[m.","body":" Ex 28:32, edge, cf. Albr:ZAW xvi (1896), 76], lip, speech, edge;&#8212;abs. &#180;[[שׂ]]: Ge 11:1 +, cstr. [[שְׂפַת]] v:Ge 11:7 +; sf. [[שְׂפָתוֹ]] 1Ki 7:23 +, etc.; oftener du. [[שְׂפָתַיִם]] Is 6:5 +, cstr. [[שִׂפְתֵי]] Ps 12:4 +; sf. [[שְׂפָתַי]] Je 17:16 +, sf. 3 mpl. [[שְׂפָתֵימוֹ]] Ps 59:13, Ps 140:4, Ps 140:10, etc.; pl. (poet. and late) cstr. [[שִׂפְתוֹת]] Ec 10:12, sf. [[שִׂפְתוֹתֶיךָ]] etc. Ps 45:3, Ps 59:8, Is 59:3, Ct So 4:3, So 4:11, So 5:13;&#8212;","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"1.","body":" lip: ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"a.","body":" usu. (c. 108 t.) human organ of speech (oft. &#8214;[[פֶּה ]], [[לָשׁוֹן]] rarely [only late poetry] [[חֵח]]: 10 t. Jb; 25 t. Psalm Psalm; 45 t. Pr): (1) Is 29:13, Le 5:4 (P), Job 13:6, Mal 2:6, Ps 12:5, Pr 5:3 +; &#180;[[דַּל שׂ]]: Ps 141:3 (v. [[דָּל]]); &#180;[[אִישׁ שׂ]]: Job 11:2 = a talker, &#180;[[אֱוִיל שׂ]]: Pr 10:8 = one talking folly, so v:Pr 10:10 (MT; but v. Toy); [[טְמֵא שְׂפָתַיִם]] Is 6:5, Is 6:5 cf. v:Is 6:7, Da 10:16; &#180;[[עֲרַל שׂ]]: Ex 6:12, Ex 6:30 (P; unskilled in speech); &#180;[[עִקֵּשׁ שׂ]]: Ex 19:1; &#180;[[פּׂתֶה שׂ]]: Ex 20:19 v. [[[פָּתָה]]] p. 834; &#180;[[מוֹחָא שׂ]]: i.e. utterance, De 23:24, Je 17:16, Nu 30:13 (P), Ps 89:35, &#180;[[רוּחַ שׂ]]: Is 11:4 (of Mess. kg.), &#180;[[דְּבַר שׂ]]: Ps 59:13, Pr 14:23 +, = mere, empty, word 2Ki 18:20 = Is 36:5; &#180;[[תְּבוּאַת שׂ]]: Pr 18:20, &#180;[[נוב שׂ]]: Is 57:19 (thanksgiving), cf. Ho 14:3 (LXX SyrVer and most [[פְּדִי]] for [[פָּרִים]]); of flattery, &#180;[[חֵלֶק שׂ]]: Pr 7:21, [[שְׂפַת חֲלָקוֹת]] Ps 12:3, Ps 12:4; cf. [[שִׂפְתֵי מִרְמָה]] Ps 17:1, [[שֶׁקֶר]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Ps 31:9 + 4 t., [[שְׂפַת אָוֶן]] Pr 17:4; poison beneath (cf. [[לָשׁוֹן]]) Ps 140:4 (fig.); &#180;[[פֶּשַׁע שׂ]]: Pr 12:13; &#180;[[לְזוּת שׂ]]: Pr 4:24; [[אֱמֶת]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Pr 12:19, [[יׇ֑תֶר]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Pr 17:7, [[חֶדֶק]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Pr 16:13, [[דַּעַת]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Pr 14:7, Pr 20:15; &#180;[[חֵן שׂ]]: Pr 22:11; [[שָׂפָה בְרוּרָה]] Zep 3:9; [[רְנׇנוֹת]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Ps 63:5 i.e. lips that shout for joy; c. vbs.: &#180;[[פָּתַח שׂ]]: (to speak) Job 11:5, Job 30:20 (Gi v:21), cf. Ps 51:17, &#180;[[מִפְתַּח שׂ]]: Pr 8:6; &#180;[[פָּשַׁק שׂ]]: Pr 13:3 i.e. prate; [[מָֽלְאוּ זַעַם]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Is 30:27; &#180;[[שׂ]]: subj. of [[דִּבֶּר]] Is 59:3, Pr 24:2; &#180;[[נׇשָׂא עַל־שׂ]]: Ps 16:14; &#180;[[קָרַץ שׂ]]: Pr 16:30 = backbite; &#180;[[אָטַם שׂ]]: Pr 17:28 = keep silence, so &#180;[[חָשַׂח שׂ]]: Pr 10:19, [[כָּלָא]] &#180;[[שׂ]]: Ps 40:10. &#134; (2) lips moving in speech, c. [[נוּעַ]] 1Sa 1:13, [[נִיד]] Job 16:5. &#134; (3) transition to mng. speech, [[עָלָה עַל־שְׂפַת לָשׁוֹן]] Ez Eze 36:3; = ability to speak Job 12:20. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"b.","body":" organ of laughter Job 8:21. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"c.","body":" of insulting grimace &#180;[[הִפְטִיר בְּשׂ]]: Ps 22:8. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"d.","body":" quivering in terror Hb Hab 3:16. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"e.","body":" feature of beauty Ct So 4:3 (scarlet). ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"f.","body":" place of bridle 2Ki 19:28 = Is 37:29 (v. [[מֶתֶג]]). &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"g.","body":" receiving kiss Pr 24:26 cf. Ct So 4:11 and (in fig.) So 7:10. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"h.","body":" of divine speech, &#180;[[מִחְוַת שׂ]]: Job 23:12, &#180;[[דְּבַר שׂ]]: Ps 17:4. &#134; ","content":"definition","show":"block"},{"title":"2.","body":" language (v. [[לָשׁוֹן]]), Ge 11:1, Ge 11:6, Ge 11:7, Ge 11:7, Ge 11:9, Ps 81:6; &#180;[[עַם עִמְקֵי שׂ]]: Ez Eze 3:5, Eze 3:6, Is 33:19, &#180;[[לַעֲגֵי שׂ]]: Is 28:11; [[שְׂפַת כְּנַעַן]] Is 19:18 (i.e. Hebrew). ","conte